### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3001/health

### 建立報名
POST http://localhost:3001/api/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "王小明",
  "email": "xiaoming@example.com",
  "phone": "0912345678"
}

### 測試重複 Email（應該會失敗）
POST http://localhost:3001/api/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "李小華",
  "email": "xiaoming@example.com",
  "phone": "0923456789"
}

### 取得所有報名（第一頁，每頁 10 筆）
GET http://localhost:3001/api/signup?page=1&limit=10

### 取得第二頁
GET http://localhost:3001/api/signup?page=2&limit=10

### 更新電話（需替換實際 ID）
PATCH http://localhost:3001/api/signup/YOUR_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "0987654321"
}

### 更新狀態
PATCH http://localhost:3001/api/signup/YOUR_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "confirmed"
}

### 刪除報名（需替換實際 ID）
DELETE http://localhost:3001/api/signup/YOUR_ID_HERE

